info.name: FOGProject <= 1.5.10.1673 - Authentication Bypass
author: oleveloper
info.description: FOGProject version 1.5.10.1673 suffers from an authentication bypass vulnerability that allows unauthenticated users to access the management interface without proper authentication. This can lead to unauthorized access to system configuration, host management, and potentially database information.
info.impact: Unauthenticated attackers can bypass authentication to access the FOGProject management interface and retrieve sensitive system configuration and host management information.
info.remediation: Upgrade FOGProject to a version later than 1.5.10.1673 that implements proper authentication on all management endpoints.
